: 30px; margin-bottom: 0;">Buy the rumor, sell the =E2=80=98Weekend Update=
=E2=80=99 segment</h2><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When Elon Musk does Bitc=
oin things, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/237996=
