rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> famously a jok=
e</a>, and Elon Musk enjoys jokes, and people enjoy following along with El=
on Musk=E2=80=99s jokes at home, and so when Elon Musk does a Dogecoin joke=
 Dogecoin goes up.=C2=A0There is an obvious =E2=80=9Crich famous weird guy =
with a fandom=E2=80=9D effect.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other=
 hand, is there a business fundamentals case? Will Tesla accept Dogecoin as=
 payment? Will it be legal tender on Mars? Sure, I dunno, whatever,=C2=A0bu=
