r: #ccc;"> leaned hard on the =E2=80=9Cjoke=E2=80=9D side</a>:</p><blockquo=
te><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Dogecoin, the fifth most valuable cryptocur=
rency, retreated from an all-time high after billionaire Elon Musk, appeari=
ng on =E2=80=9CSaturday Night Live,=E2=80=9D jokingly called it =E2=80=9Ca =
hustle.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The altcoin had surpassed =
73 cents on Saturday before dropping to 46.01 cents as of 8:08 a.m. in New =
York Sunday, a 35% decline in 24 hours, according to pricing from CoinGecko=
. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Musk was asked repeatedly durin=
g the =E2=80=9CWeekend Update=E2=80=9D segment to explain what Dogecoin is.=
 After reciting multiple facts about the cryptocurrency in the character of=
 a financial expert, he was asked if Dogecoin was a =E2=80=9Chustle.=E2=80=
=9D He responded, =E2=80=9Cyeah, it=E2=80=99s a hustle.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6<=
/p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">An earlier Dogecoin reference came during t=
he opening monologue where his mother, Maye Musk, joined him on stage. The =
author and model said she was excited about her Mother=E2=80=99s Day gift, =
and she hoped it=E2=80=99s not Dogecoin -- to which he said, =E2=80=9Cit is=
.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I want to emphasize=
 again that I understand nothing, but, like =E2=80=A6=C2=A0if you bet big o=
n Dogecoin heading into =E2=80=9CSaturday Night Live,=E2=80=9D and then dum=
ped your Dogecoins because you didn=E2=80=99t like what you heard on =E2=80=
=9CSaturday Night Live,=E2=80=9D what=C2=A0<em>were=C2=A0</em>you hoping to=
 hear? Like, =E2=80=9CSaturday Night Live=E2=80=9D is a comedy program. Elo=
n Musk was going to make jokes about Dogecoin. That was pretty much the bes=
t you could hope for, from Elon Musk on =E2=80=9CSaturday Night Live,=E2=80=
