ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; =
background-color: #ccc;">makes nitrile gloves</a>, does other miscellaneous=
 projects, and says =E2=80=9CTransforming Civilization=E2=80=9D at the top =
of its web page. I have to say, I really admire this trade; this is how you=
 do postmodern finance. I think the trade is:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-ty=
pe: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bo=
ttom: 5px;">Accumulate a bunch of Dogecoins.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bot=
tom: 5px;">Go to Elon Musk and say =E2=80=9Chey would you accept payment in=
 Dogecoins to do a=C2=A0Dogecoin stunt?=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin=
-bottom: 5px;">Elon Musk is like =E2=80=9Csure, I love Dogecoins, and stunt=
s.=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You pay him some Dogec=
oins to launch some stuff into space.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5p=
x;">You and he both announce that SpaceX is accepting Dogecoin for payment =
for a rocket payload that has something to do with the moon.[1]</li>=09<li =
style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">=E2=80=9CLook: SpaceX is accepting Dogecoin! =
Institutional adoption! Dogecoin is a useful currency! There are applicatio=
ns! Dogecoin will be the official currency of space travel! It will be wide=
ly adopted throughout the galaxy! If you are traveling to Mars you will nee=
d to convert some dollars into Dogecoin!=E2=80=9D You know, that sort of th=
ing.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The value of your remaining s=
tash of Dogecoins goes up a lot.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If y=
ou have 10 million Dogecoins, what you want to do is=C2=A0<em>spend a milli=
on of them</em>, because demonstrating that you can spend Dogecoins is a go=
od way to prove that they are useful and thus make the value of your remain=
ing 9 million Dogecoins go up. What you particularly want to do is=C2=A0<em=
>spend your Dogecoins at an Elon Musk store</em>, because that will focus a=
 lot of attention on the fact that you can spend Dogecoins, because people =
pay a lot of attention to the Elon Musk stores. And you want to spend them =
on the most high-profile and stunty Elon Musk store available, which is pro=
bably shooting a rocket to the moon.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Dogeco=
in is =E2=80=94=C2=A0so much postmodern crypto/GameStop finance is, really =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0finance with the cash flows abstracted away. In traditional =
finance, you have a=C2=A0thing with some more or less uncertain stream of f=
uture=C2=A0cash flows, and the value of the thing is the present value of i=
ts future cash flows, filtered through some large amount of uncertainty and=
 psychology and behavior and greed and fear and technical factors and fund =
flows etc. The skill set is some combination of understanding the cash flow=
s and understanding the psychology.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In post=
modern finance the psychology is the only thing. For sort of accidental pat=
h-dependence reasons, the people making fortunes in this world are often=C2=
=A0<em>finance=C2=A0</em>people, quant traders who saw the rise of crypto a=
nd thought =E2=80=9Cthat=E2=80=99s like what I do now, but without any fund=
amentals,=E2=80=9D and who jumped on it. Fine. But it is not obvious that t=
his is the right, or only, skill set. Really if postmodern finance is prima=
rily a matter of=C2=A0mass psychology, isn=E2=80=99t it =E2=80=A6=C2=A0mark=
eting? Advertising? Isn=E2=80=99t the right skill set not, like, =E2=80=9Ci=
dentify technical patterns in charts=E2=80=9D but rather =E2=80=9Cthink of =
good stunts that will make people want to buy a content-free product that y=
ou happen to be selling=E2=80=9D? If you are a Dogecoin trader and you=E2=
=80=99re not spending some Dogecoins to get Elon Musk to put out a press re=
lease with the words =E2=80=9CDogecoin=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cmoon=E2=80=9D =
and =E2=80=9Crocket=E2=80=9D in it, you might be doing it wrong.</p><h2 sty=
le=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial, Helve=
tica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bottom-widt=
h: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 30px;=
 margin-bottom: 0;">Elsewhere in Elon Musk</h2><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"=
>Well there=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/23799615.262686/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhldmVyZ2UuY29tLzIwMjEvNS83LzIyNDI0NTk=
