CEO Elon Musk has been overstating the capabilities of the company=E2=80=99=
s advanced driver assist system, the company=E2=80=99s director of Autopilo=
t software told the California Department of Motor Vehicles. The comments c=
ame from a memo released by legal transparency group PlainSite, which obtai=
ned the documents from a public records request. ...</p><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CElon=E2=80=99s tweet does not match engineering reality =
per CJ. Tesla is at Level 2 currently,=E2=80=9D the California DMV said in =
the memo about its March 9th conference call with Tesla representatives, in=
cluding the director of Autopilot software CJ Moore. Level 2 technology ref=
ers to a semi-automated driving system, which requires supervision by a hum=
an driver.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In an earnings call in Jan=
uary, Musk told investors that he was =E2=80=9Chighly confident the car wil=
l be able to drive itself with reliability in excess of human this year.=E2=
=80=9D (It would appear the DMV was referring to these January comments, wh=
ich Moore misunderstood as a tweet from Musk.) =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin: 16px 0;">Tesla is unlikely to achieve Level 5 (L5) autonomy, in which =
its cars can drive themselves anywhere, under any conditions, without any h=
uman supervision, by the end of 2021, Tesla representatives told the DMV.</=
p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Is this securities fraud? Meh. =
We have talked a lot recently about the notion that influential visionary s=
tartup founders are expected to do a certain amount of optimistic truth-str=
etching,=C2=A0that seeing the future so clearly that you convince yourself =
it=E2=80=99s here already is part of the job. Occasionally actual startup f=
ounders <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23799615.2=
62686/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDUtM=
DYvZG9nZWNvaW4taXMtdXAtYmVjYXVzZS1pdC1zLWZ1bm55/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB53=
106a0e" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000=
000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bot=
tom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> g=
